 classical region. Chaos can result from Neptune's\ninteractions with Uranus, exciting the cold KBOs and placing additional\nconstraints. Finally, we discuss how to interpret our constraints in the\ncontext of the full, complex dynamical history of the solar system.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 27 Feb 2012 21:00:03 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 16 Apr 2012 19:24:32 GMT"}],"update_date":"2012-04-17"}
