fered by the multipath, the effect of imbalances on monobit receivers in\nfading channels is slight. I\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 28 Feb 2012 07:55:47 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 7 May 2012 13:04:27 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 4 Jun 2013 08:57:54 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-06-05"}
