 Its equilibrium\ntemperature of 1517 +/- 29 K is within 60K of that of the extensively-studied\nplanet HD 209458b.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 28 Feb 2012 15:26:28 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 29 Feb 2012 09:15:21 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-04"}
